We got 6 python files:

1. main.py -  entry point of the app. Intialises the the Tkinter UI

2. database_manager.py - handles sql database operations.

3. music_player.py - controls music playback using pygame.mixer. handles play, pause, resume and stop.

4. ui_manager.py - builds GUI with Tkinter.

5. song.py - defines the song class

6. album.py - defines album class.







